asset.author: Camp Chef
asset.hookText:
www.CampChef.com

Ideal for compact, lightweight cooking, the Stryker stove is built for easy cooking on or off the trail. Heat Ring technology creates larger surface area that captures and transfers heat for a rapid boil. Heat Ring technology increases heat efficiency by 30%, taking only two minutes to boil a ½ liter of water while reducing overall fuel consumption. The Stryker stove comes complete with a tri-legged stand, burner with matchless ignition and an insulated 1.3 liter pot. Components pack tightly inside the pot weighing only 8.3 ounces (not including fuel). Mesh carry bag included.
